1. Any DNS change requires:
   - Full login to registrar
   - Full login to Vercel
   - Manual verification of nameservers
   - Manual verification of A + CNAME records

2. Any repo change requires:
   - Authenticated GitHub login
   - Branch protection approval
   - PR review (even if you are the only reviewer)

3. Any domain configuration change must be logged:
   - Date
   - Time
   - What changed
   - Why it changed
